      <scopecontent id="aspace_fba04083dd86c59da21a71e106a3cfe0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, program information, student evaluations, financial papers, and subject files of the Yale Summer and Special Programs documenting the activities and operations of the American Economic Association Summer Minority Program at Yale, which ended in 1982.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_20d1a79524fccc348d35e7866dfca44c">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
